rder-top:1.0000pt solid rgb(235,235,235);mso-border-top-alt:0.7500pt solid rgb(235,235,235);border-bottom:1.0000pt solid rgb(235,235,235);mso-border-bottom-alt:0.7500pt solid rgb(235,235,235);background:rgb(66,155,216);" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;background:rgb(66,155,216);" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(66,155,216);mso-shading:rgb(66,155,216);" >专业技能</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(66,155,216);mso-shading:rgb(66,155,216);" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><table class=MsoNormalTable  style="border-collapse:collapse;width:468.9500pt;margin-left:29.6500pt;mso-table-layout-alt:fixed;mso-padding-alt:0.7500pt 0.7500pt 0.7500pt 0.7500pt ;" ><tr><td width=625  valign=center  style="width:468.9500pt;padding:0.7500pt 0.7500pt 0.7500pt 9.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:13.5000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >1、熟练使用Srping，SpringMVC，MyBatis等后台常用框架；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:13.5000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:13.5000pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >2、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >熟练使用Oracle、Mysql等主流数据库，熟悉redis的工作原理，熟练编写简单的SQL语句，</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:13.5000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >具备一定的数据库优化能力；&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:13.5000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para