pan></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >2、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >在统计分析模块中，运用HighCharts图标库和POI报表技术对销售退货、销售趋势进行分析统计；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >3、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >库存管理模块:库存查询、库存变更、基于quartz框架完成的库存预警模块；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >4、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >权限管理模块,包括密码重置、用户角色设置、角色设置和基于Shiro实现的角色权限设置等。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >5、</span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >进行代码的重构优化，如利用泛型技术重构和抽取以提高代码重用度。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:16.5000pt;" ><td width=122  valign=center  style="width:92.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=433  valign=center  style="width:324.8000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目简介</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >:</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >为了实现山西沃特海默公司的人、财、物、供、产、销全面结合、实时反馈、动态协调、降低成本，为了更直观地了解公司的运营状况及其他基本信息，为了给决策者提供更有力的理论的依据，进而开发了该项目。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >该项目采用SpringMVC&nbsp;+&nbsp;Spring&nbsp;+&nbsp;MyBatis&nbsp;等框架搭建的传统架构，同时结合easyUI、JQuery等前端技术、CXF框架、POI报表技术和WebService远程调用技术。项目共包含以下模块：基本信息管理、人事管理、采购管理、生产管理、销售管理、仓库管理、统计分析、权限设置。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:314.7000pt;" ><td width=622  valign=center  style="width:466.9000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><table class=MsoNormalTable  style="border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:48.6000pt;mso-table-layout-alt:fixed;mso-padding-alt:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><tr style="height:16.5000pt;" ><td width=122  valign=center  style="width:92.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  align=center  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >互易书城</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width=433  valign=center  style="width:324.8000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:22.0000pt;" ><td width=122  valign=center  style="width:92.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  align=center  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=433  valign=center  style="width:324.8000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >责任描述</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >：商品类目的管理、注册登录模块、商品搜索和商品展示。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >１、使用maven技术管理项目，有效地提高了开发代码效率；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >２、在进行商品搜索时，使用solr构建索引库，有效地减轻了数据库压力；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >３、使用redis作为中间健进行缓存；</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:105.2500pt;" ><td width=122  valign=center  style="width:92.2000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=433  valign=center  style="width:324.8000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目简介</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >:</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >互易书城是采用C2C运营模式的电子书籍商城，面向所有的写作工作者，由店主自主创建书店，上传资源并定价，其他客户根据自身需要购买下载资源。店主入驻书城，享有书城提供的服务，客户可以在商城浏览商品、下单等，后台管理人员可以在后台管理系统中管理商品、订单、会员等。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目分前台系统和后台管理系统，前台系统主要有：门户、商品搜索和展示、订单、购物车、登录注册、支付等常见模块；后台只要有：商品管理、系统管理等模块。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目采用SpringMVC&nbsp;+&nbsp;Spring&nbsp;+&nbsp;MyBatis&nbsp;等框架搭建的分布式架构，easyUI、JQuery等前端技术，运用Nginx反向代理服务器，采用Redis非关系型数据库作为缓存技术支持。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:181.1500pt;" ><td width=622  valign=center  style="width:466.9000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><table class=MsoNormalTable  style="border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:48.6000pt;mso-table-layout-alt:fixed;mso-padding-alt:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><tr style="height:16.5000pt;" ><td width=123  valign=center  style="width:92.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  align=center  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >星宇</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >服饰商城</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width=432  valign=center  style="width:324.6000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:16.5000pt;" ><td width=123  valign=center  style="width:92.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=432  valign=center  style="width:324.6000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >责任描述：</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >、</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >参与项目的功能分析和设计讨论，负责前台系统模块、搜索模块。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >、</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >根据所需求的业务进行开发，代码编写，实现功能。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:16.5000pt;" ><td width=123  valign=center  style="width:92.4000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=432  valign=center  style="width:324.6000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目简介：</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >新星服饰商城是商城平台网站，系统包括：后台管理系统，前台系统，会员系统，订单系统，搜索系统，单点登录系统等。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目采用springmvc+spring+mybatis框架，数据库为MySQL，管理系统之间的调用，采用分布式文件系统作为图片上传的服务器</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:8.8500pt;" ><td width=622  valign=center  style="width:466.9000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><table class=MsoNormalTable  style="border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:48.6000pt;mso-table-layout-alt:fixed;mso-padding-alt:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><tr style="height:4.5000pt;" ><td width=124  valign=center  style="width:93.1000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  align=center  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >新雅电子商务</span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width=431  valign=center  style="width:323.9000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:72.0500pt;" ><td width=124  valign=center  style="width:93.1000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  align=center  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p></td><td width=431  valign=center  style="width:323.9000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >责任描述：</span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >、</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >参与项目的功能分析和设计讨论，负责</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >面向用户的部分中的</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >线购物</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >、搜索模块。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >、</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >根据所需求的业务进行开发，代码编写，实现功能。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:16.5000pt;" ><td width=124  valign=center  style="width:93.1000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ;" ><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></td><td width=431  valign=center  style="width:323.9000pt;padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 10.5000pt ;" ><p class=40  style="margin-right:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;layout-grid-mode:char;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >项目描述：</span></b><b><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=40  style="margin-right:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;layout-grid-mode:char;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >随着社会的不断进步，网络的不断发展，越来越多的网上商城相继出现，公司为适应发展，扩大业务，提升品牌影响力，决定开发此系统。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=40  style="margin-right:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;text-indent:18.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;layout-grid-mode:char;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >系统主要包括两个部分，一部分是面向用户的部分，包括：购物、订单</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >、搜索等模块</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >；另一部分是商城管理部分，包括：商品的管理、订单的管理、用户管理</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >等</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=40  style="margin-right:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;text-indent:20.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;layout-grid-mode:char;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >该项没有</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Eclipse</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >+</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >mysql</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >+</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Struts2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >+</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Hibernate</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >+</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Spring</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:9.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >搭建而成的开发环境。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></table><p class=33  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;word-break:break-all;text-autospace:ideograph-other;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;line-height:15.0000pt;" ><span style="